<h2>Introduction</h2>

<p> It is clear at this point that we will not make our goal of Febuary 15th for 
  the 2.16 release. However, the Bugzilla tree is now frozen and is only accepting 
  bugs that have been targeted as 2.16 blockers, and things are moving quickly now,
  so it looks reasonable that we won't have to delay again beyond March 1st, and
  will probably release sooner if the right things fall into place before then.</p>


